## ğŸš€ Usage

```bash
python topsis.py <input_file> <weights> <impacts> <output_file>
```

Example:

```bash
python topsis.py data.csv "1,2,1,1" "+,+,-,+" result.csv
```

---

## âš ï¸ Limitations

- Categorical data not supported  
- Missing values not allowed  
- Weights must be positive  
- Impacts must be '+' or '-'  

